pullRequest.title: Fix #8845: Enable parsing for Locus Map coordinate format
pullRequest.bodyText: We now separately parse the coordinates for each supported delimiter instead of normalizing the delimiters and parsing the coordinates once. Thus, we support parsing of coordinates with separators that contain other delimiters, e.g., the Locus Map format: Nxx° yy.zzz', Exx° yy.zzz'.
